I have really enjoyed watching Andy over the past two weeks and this is the first time I have seen him with his ‘mojo’ back since Wimbledon.

There have been spells here when he has played superb clay-court tennis, with his movement outstanding and that backhand better than ever. Whatever the result today I think it will put him in extremely good shape for the grass-court season.

