Can he beat Nadal? I do not sense any great vulnerability in the Spaniard, although his serve has not been quite as strong as previously. Clearly he is the solid favourite but if Andy manages to dictate for long enough then he has a chance.

A word of warning is that if the predicted hot weather materialises that is good for Rafa, as it will add zip and bounce to his ground-strokes.

